Step 2: Declare variables name, hourly rate salary, deduction rate, gross rate, deduction, gross pay, net pay, hours worked
Step 3: Input variables for name, Hourly Rate Salary, Deduction Rate
Step 4: Multiply hourly rate salary & hours worked
